接是可点击的文本，可以将您重定向到其他页面。</p><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#tag"> </a><a>标签</a></h2><p><a>或锚标记定义超链接。</a><a><br></a></p><pre> <code>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codewithharry.com/&quot;&gt;Visit CodeWithHarry.com!&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#form"> </a>形式</h2><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#sample-form"> </a>样表</h2><p>表单用于收集用户的输入，一般将用户的数据发送到服务器进行进一步处理。<br></p><pre> <code>&lt;form action=&quot;/action.php&quot; method=&quot;post&quot;&gt; Name: &lt;input name=&quot;name&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Age: &lt;input max=&quot;90&quot; min=&quot;1&quot; name=&quot;age&quot; step=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;number&quot; value=&quot;18&quot; /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;select name=&quot;gender&quot;&gt; &lt;option selected=&quot;selected&quot; value=&quot;male&quot;&gt;Male&lt;/option&gt; &lt;option value=&quot;female&quot;&gt;Female&lt;/option&gt; &lt;/select&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;input checked=&quot;checked&quot; name=&quot;newsletter&quot; type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;daily&quot; /&gt; Daily &lt;input name=&quot;newsletter&quot; type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;weekly&quot; /&gt; Weekly&lt;br /&gt; &lt;textarea cols=&quot;20&quot; name=&quot;comments&quot; rows=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Comment&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;label&gt;&lt;input name=&quot;terms&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;tandc&quot; /&gt;Accept terms&lt;/label&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;Submit&quot; /&gt; &lt;/form&gt;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#characters-amp-symbols"> </a>字符和符号</h2><p>有些符号不直接出现在键盘上，但有一些方法可以在 HTML 文档中使用它们。 我们可以通过实体名称、十进制或十六进制值来显示它们。</p><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#copyright-symbol-%C2%A9"> </a> 版权符号 (©)</h2><pre> <code>&amp;copy;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#less-than-lt"> </a>小于 (&lt;)</h2><pre> <code>&amp;lt</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#greater-than-gt"> </a>大于 (&gt;)</h2><pre> <code>&amp;gt;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#ampersand-amp"> </a>符号 (&amp;)</h2><pre> <code>&amp;amp;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#dollar-"> </a>美元 ($)</h2><pre> <code>&amp;dollar;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#random-text"> </a>随机文本</h2><pre><code>Elon Musk Elon Reeve Musk FRS is an entrepreneur and business magnate. He is the founder, CEO, and Chief Engineer at SpaceX; early stage investor, CEO, and Product Architect of Tesla, Inc.; founder of The Boring Company; and co-founder of Neuralink and OpenAI. A centibillionaire, Musk is one of the richest people in the world.</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#semantic-elements"> </a>语义元素</h2><p>语义元素是那些可以自我描述的元素，即从它们的名字本身，你就可以理解它们的含义。</p><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#tag"> </a>标签</h2><p>它定义了文档中的一个部分<br></p><pre><code>&lt;section&gt;This is a section&lt;/section&gt;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#tag"> </a>标签</h2><p>它代表独立的内容<br></p><pre><code>&lt;article&gt; Enter your data here &lt;/article&gt;</code></pre><h2><a href="https://dev.to/backlinkss/html-cheatsheet-11pl#tag"> </a>标签</h2><p>用于在侧边栏中放置内容<br></p><pre><code>&lt;aside&gt; Your data &lt;/aside&gt;</code></pre><p> <i>👉 For More Details Visit Here : <a href="https://www.backlinkss.link/2022/12/html-cheatsheet.html">BackLinks</a></i> <b>👉有关更多详细信息，请访问此处：<a href="https://www.backlinkss.link/2022/12/html-cheatsheet.html">反向链接</a></b></p> <br>
